          "issue": "Operating expenses stored as a negative number (-18,299,805). The validator computes GP - OpEx_stored = GP - (-18,299,805) = GP + 18,299,805, which yields ~45.76M vs reported OpInc 9.16M, hence +399.57% drift. Fix: store OpEx as positive magnitude."
        },
